          "validation_ok": true,
          "errors": [],
          "repaired": false,
          "latency_ms": 6960,
          "unit_kind": "paragraph"
        },
        "text": "The consultation also highlights the risks that can arise when companies use personal data to personalise offers, particularly if such practices exploit consumer vulnerabilities.",
        "chunk_meta": {
          "section_id": "s4",
          "section_path": [
            "Introduction",
            "Use of personal data in the context of insurance (risk-based underwriting)"
