          "repaired": false,
          "latency_ms": 3825,
          "unit_kind": "paragraph"
        },
        "text": "Insurance Europe is the European insurance and reinsurance federation. Through its 39 member bodies — the national insurance associations — it represents insurance and reinsurance undertakings active in Europe and advocates for policies and conditions that support the sector in delivering value to individuals, businesses, and the broader economy.",
